text: Joseph Damer (1676–1737), of Dorchester, Dorset, was an English politician. He was a Member of Parliament (MP) for Dorchester 1722 to 1727. ==References== Category:1676 births Category:1737 deaths Category:People from Dorchester, Dorset Category:Members of the Parliament of Great Britain for English constituencies
